    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, trim, then chop your <strong>spring onion[s] </strong>roughly</p><p>Grate your <strong>cheddar flavour block[s]</strong></p><p>Break your <strong>lasagne sheets</strong> in the bag into bite-sized pieces</p><p>Wash your <strong>spinach</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p>",
