    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once hot, add 250ml<span class=\"text-purple\"> [375ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[500ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> to the dish with your <strong>Dijon mustard</strong>, <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong>, <strong>single creamy soy</strong>, <strong>spinach </strong>and your <strong>Chinese rice wine</strong></p><p>Add your <strong>roasted garlic paste</strong>, <strong>chopped spring onion</strong> and your <strong>butternut squash cubes</strong> with a very generous grind of <strong>black</strong> <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up</p>",
