    {
      "instruction": "<p>After 15 min, remove the dish from the oven and give it a good stir</p><p>Top with the <strong>grated cheeze</strong></p><p>Return the dish to the oven and cook, uncovered, for a final 25 min or until the pasta is tender – this is your<strong> one-pot plant-based butternut squash & spinach lasagne</strong></p>",
