    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the lasagne is almost done, wash your<strong> lettuce</strong>, then pat it dry with<strong> </strong>kitchen paper and shred roughly</p><p>Add your <strong>balsamic vinegar</strong> to a large bowl with a generous drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Add the<strong> shredded lettuce</strong> to the bowl and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>dressed salad</strong></p><p>Pick your <strong>basil leaves </strong>from their stems, discard the stems</p>",
